<div class="cooking-container">
  <h1 class="text-center border-bottom py-4 font-weight-bold">やさしい味わいの豚汁</h1>
  <br>
  <div class="d-flex flex-wrap px-5 py-5 border-bottom">
    <div class="m-auto">
      <img src="https://cooking-records.herokuapp.com/images/1.jpg">
    </div>
    <div class="py-3 ingredients-content">
      <h2 class="font-weight-bold">材料</h2>
      <ul class="w-100 mt-4 ingredients">
        <li>豚肉 100g</li>
        <li>大根 1/2本</li>
        <li>人参 1本</li>
        <li>ねぎ 1/2本</li>
        <li>味噌 大さじ3杯</li>
        <li>醤油 大さじ1杯</li>
        <li>塩 少々</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="px-5 ">
    <h1 class="py-4 font-weight-bold">料理記録</h1>
    <div class="d-flex border-bottom py-4">
      <%= link_to my_cookings_path, data: { turbolinks: false } do %>
        <img src="https://cooking-records.herokuapp.com/images/1.jpg" class="comment-img" width="80" height="80">
      <% end %>
      <span class="pl-5 comment">豚肉のコクとごぼうの香り、野菜の甘みで奥行きのある味わい。</span>
    </div>
    <div class="d-flex border-bottom py-4">
      <%= link_to my_cookings_path, data: { turbolinks: false } do %>
        <img src="https://cooking-records.herokuapp.com/images/1.jpg" class="comment-img" width="80" height="80">
      <% end %>
      <span class="pl-5 comment">やわらかな豚肉、野菜の甘みで奥行きのある味わい。</span>
    </div>
    <div class="d-flex border-bottom py-4">
      <%= link_to my_cookings_path, data: { turbolinks: false } do %>
        <img src="https://cooking-records.herokuapp.com/images/1.jpg" class="comment-img" width="80" height="80">
      <% end %>
      <span class="pl-5 comment">野菜の甘みで奥行きのある味わい。</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
